### Steps to reproduce
import { transformURL } from "./utils/file";
(function(imageDesc) {
  const imageNativeSet = imageDesc.set;
  Object.defineProperty(Image.prototype, "src", {
    async set(url) {
      url = await transformURL(url); // 将不能直接显示的URL转成base64
      imageNativeSet.call(this, url); // 重新设置IMAGE -> SRC = base64
    },
  });
}) (Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(Image.prototype, "src"));

### What is expected?
图片的加载内容是转码后的base64
exp: <div style="url(xxxx.jpg)" />   => <div style="url(base64)" />

### What is actually happening?
1. async set function被执行两次；
2. 并不能用base64替代转码前的URL，图片加载报错；

---
像这种全局的图片属性(src)监听并重写set，我的理解应该只对 new Image().src = "xxxx.jpg" 起作用，可为何在Vue里面对css设置的图片属性(background-image: url("xxxx.jpg"))也生效呢，Vue是否有做了代理(proxy)？

Thanks.

